":"TVB新聞寫啲唔寫啲<br />\n呢次包機唔會接新求助既武漢港人"},{"pid":"075918ae68f9f31dae3cbb70a7e4b572405b2603","tid":1937042,"uid":85358,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"武漢0確診仲安全過香港做乜仲要包機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b5669eb957a1308173b2c56e596419c12de6ca","tid":1937042,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T15:52:44.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政制及內地事務局局長聶德權表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">第二批接載滯留湖北港人的包機，會在下周三及周四出發。</span><br />\n<br />\n聶德權表示，因近日疫情迅速發展，要衡量風險，決定調整第二批包機的安排<span style=\"color: red;\">，今次行動將不包括武漢市新增的求助個案，政府駐武漢辦會繼續協助滯留的港人。</span><br />\n<br />\n武漢市以外地區回港人士，只須家居檢疫，武漢市回港則仍要住檢疫中心。上包機前，要進行健康評估和接受當地政府查核，確保不是確診者或緊密接觸者，登機前會多次量體溫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=385182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385182&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcMeYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=f5547275\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385182&h=a9d88ce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=385182</a>"},{"pid":"b030f4898a5d5126703b3d166a81e5bbaa324462","tid":1937042,"uid":68226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"075918ae68f9f31dae3cbb70a7e4b572405b2603","tid":1937042,"uid":85358,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"武漢0確診仲安全過香港做乜仲要包機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:00:13.000Z","msg":"返到黎確診 又可以賴香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa103aa6de24e63